snippet.title: Modern Greaser
snippet.description: Automotive videos have become far too serious these days.  Let Modern Greaser put a comical spin on things with his less than extensive knowledge about cars.  Watch as he pretends to educate you all about amazing vehicles, but basically ends up looking like a dumb dumb.
